{"word":"παρεισέρχομαι","slug":"παρεισέρχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παρεισέρχομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> with <a href='S:aorist tense'>aor.</a> and <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>to come</i> or <i>go in beside</i> or <i>secretly</i>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/>"}]}